{"tid":615620,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"合照變成了獨照","createTime":"2018-04-03T14:09:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-03T20:50:19.000Z","uid":157807,"like":3,"dislike":162,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"128c0af08e4ff082e0c23bdc0ee618ea1846ceb1","tid":615620,"uid":157807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T14:09:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4d031a614b46d50ba6ca4fa88adabcb84c43161","tid":615620,"uid":96485,"like":77,"dislike":2,"score":75,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T14:14:45.000Z","msg":"你覺得自己無做錯嘢咁又做乜要講大話<br />\n原本唔係你錯，而家就係變成你錯<br />\n<br />\n要死嘅話<br />\n你覺得對得住生你出嚟嘅兩老？<br />\n對得住陪你大嘅朋友？<br />\n對得住你聲稱仲愛緊你嘅男朋友？<br />\n<br />\n你真係好幼稚"},{"pid":"1fdcb5800be865467bfb489f862c659b04e6b38e","tid":615620,"uid":177089,"like":47,"dislike":1,"score":46,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T14:15:22.000Z","msg":"同第二條仔靜雞雞出街仲要講大話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84a6bfc53d1cb2a2893c14682b4cfb4e5ccc0b29","tid":615620,"uid":126690,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T14:15:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7d1f6bfe557dc64df519db25358b825b786e7ec0","tid":615620,"uid":177089,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T14:16:29.000Z","msg":"不過算啦 好多野發生咗就返唔到轉頭<br />\nlife goes on. 振作啦絲打"},{"pid":"f5d10f216663f2b8f835dd1784e87e631f04f260","tid":615620,"uid":25560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T14:18:03.000Z","msg":"停一停<br />\n諗一諗"},{"pid":"8e0bd7f9fc4e5ea11fbf9103ea470cf81716f282","tid":615620,"uid":56,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T14:19:13.000Z","msg":"講大話咪即係身有屎"},{"pid":"4933d443cf45df286af687decaadae3544a08521","tid":615620,"uid":157807,"like":0,"dislike":43,"score":-43,"quote":{"pid":"1fdcb5800be865467bfb489f862c659b04e6b38e","tid":615620,"uid":177089,"like":47,"dislike":1,"score":46,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T14:15:22.000Z","msg":"同第二條仔靜雞雞出街仲要講大話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T14:19:24.000Z","msg":"個男仔佢識 同埋真係單純朋友"},{"pid":"5222208cbe3c3c3f6202a0f3daf9adb9cdb48072","tid":615620,"uid":67976,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T14:24:27.000Z","msg":"你講大話果一刻就應該要預左有呢個結果啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n假如真係咁小事你都要講大話既<br />\n我係佢我都會覺得難保你遲啲同其他男仔單獨出街都會講大話暪住佢<br />\n<br />\n理性啲諗野啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daebef9cbf2ea65072c94d901e89b0300ac6e7e0","tid":615620,"uid":176802,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T14:24:29.000Z","msg":"問心無愧做乜講大話?<br />\n你一講大話<br />\n佢咪覺得你身有屎囉<br />\n就算你係無辜<br />\n但係你一講咗大話<br />\n佢就會對你無信任<br />\n講到尾你一講大話就已經錯哂<br />\n你坦白講咪無事"},{"pid":"52dfd5c9db9b4943a249f2a8c4930412ac22acad","tid":615620,"uid":74751,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"4933d443cf45df286af687decaadae3544a08521","tid":615620,"uid":157807,"like":0,"dislike":43,"score":-43,"quote":{"pid":"1fdcb5800be865467bfb489f862c659b04e6b38e","tid":615620,"uid":177089,"like":47,"dislike":1,"score":46,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T14:15:22.000Z","msg":"同第二條仔靜雞雞出街仲要講大話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T14:19:24.000Z","msg":"個男仔佢識 同埋真係單純朋友"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T14:24:49.000Z","msg":"信任打破左 講咩都假<br />\n王寶強夠識佢經理人 連老婆都比人砌埋"},{"pid":"caf6e739fb94aa34614808531c7ae1bdee504488","tid":615620,"uid":10214,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T14:30:15.000Z","msg":"放心 <br />\n你好快會同個男仔朋友一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雞就係雞 <br />\n你根本唔識做人"},{"pid":"0257870c654754749c1909528333bbbdc15502d3","tid":615620,"uid":109608,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T14:38:11.000Z","msg":"你講大話想人點幫？你話係單純朋友，但又要講大話，做男人完全覺得解釋唔到。<br />\n<br />\n算啦。分開咗。過多兩年睇返就會覺得好好笑。唔使自殺嘅。"},{"pid":"7487df0883b48ac0645a1914c6bc8feb8ee0bfcc","tid":615620,"uid":127061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T14:43:32.000Z","msg":"講大話等佢唔知你同第二個男仔出街<br />\n我諗你對佢嘅「愛」好打極有限"},{"pid":"3ea107b67ff72c5818bb123b395f35fe9fb336c5","tid":615620,"uid":145365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T14:45:56.000Z","msg":"就係因為佢識 先要咁絕 <br />\n仲再講大話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n死唔該死埋一邊 唔好影響到人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a91d165dada6cdb41a5595540fd60801c2b2a3e","tid":615620,"uid":118120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T14:46:34.000Z","msg":"你做錯在先喎<br />\n乜野叫男朋友都識個男仔<br />\n識都唔代表你可以咁樣唔知會男朋友之下約異性架."},{"pid":"69b19d39f26ca649388134c232f65951ab59207e","tid":615620,"uid":173397,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T14:47:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2fbf17071af71a568eb697df2803ed0bdafa78fd","tid":615620,"uid":59575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T14:48:17.000Z","msg":"快..唔好累人"},{"pid":"756a198e6bc2ae14f025a57fb238afbc7d9a7bda","tid":615620,"uid":76735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T14:49:40.000Z","msg":"好地地做乜要講大話？<br />\n咁你同啲男人同第條女wtsapp然後del對話係因為唔想你誤會有乜分別？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n鬧下架就嗌生嗌死，第時嘈離婚點算<br />\n你試下咁同你條仔講我已經搵緊方法自殺，佢實話你幼稚同叫你死都死遠啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57f81a87df19e44d15c24f7be6c1ec35f3004200","tid":615620,"uid":179340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T14:51:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c9bd463bc258dfeb91ac0be1ca11122615f6599f","tid":615620,"uid":359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T14:52:32.000Z","msg":"真係屌都廢